Trump allies Kellyanne Conway, David Urban, Johnny McEntee, Brian Ballard, =
and Charlie Kirk=E2=80=94have made directly and explicitly to the president=
-elect in recent weeks. =E2=80=9CThey=E2=80=99re spoon-feeding this to Trum=
p,=E2=80=9D
